cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use PertEMA, please cite it using the metadata below."
title: "PertEMA: Perturbation Error Meta-Assessment"
abstract: >-
  A post-hoc reliability estimator for single-cell perturbation prediction. Rather than
  build a better predictor, PertEMA scores which individual predictions can be trusted,
  using isotonic-calibrated error and split-conformal intervals over prediction-time,
  leakage-safe features, and ships a self-hostable, fully in-browser demo.
type: software
authors:
